==Finnish==
====Etymology====
From Proto-Uralic ''[[*kota]]''. Cognates include Finnish [[koti]], Estonian [[kodu]], and Hungarian [[ház]].

===Noun===
'''kota'''

#[[wigwam]]-like [[hut]]
#(''botany'') [[capsule]]

